text: The state counsellor of Myanmar () was the title of the de facto head of government of Myanmar. The office was similar to that of a prime minister. \- Note that "Suu Kyi" is a part of her given name, and that she has no family name. The office is currently vacant after the arrest of the first and only state counsellor, Aung San Suu Kyi, in the 2021 Myanmar coup d'Ã©tat. ==References== Category:Myanmar
